{
  "stem": "293.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And from his tone of voice and his way how he was talking to my mother, I realized the man is some different type of guys, and I stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he's taller-- he was taller than I, but I consider I was pretty handsome.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was extremely handsome man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I look at his eye.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He looks in my eyes, and what happened?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some thread of sympathy, some understanding between the German Catholic and the Jewish Polish officer started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was always dressed very well, so after when he was talking with my mother and explain her what he want from her, and she still hesitated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I told my mother, [NON-ENGLISH], go ahead and do it with him the business, because we need the money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, you know, I see you have a wonderful shirt, pure silk shirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I need something like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to him in German-- everything's going in German-- do you know how much cost this?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I got fresh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you know how much costs this type of shirt?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, I don't care how much costs this shirt, I would like to have a dozen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, it will cost you $5 apiece.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can be [INAUDIBLE] in zloty, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took the money and he give me the money and said, take the measurement, get me this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this way this started the friendship between Oskar Schindler and Leopold Pfefferberg what lasted till day he die in 1974 in October the 9th.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now that-- we were living in this Cracow till-- in the city of Cracow until the end of 1940.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
